        <span class="live-ticker-item"><span class="t-emoji">📦</span> Stock limité : 12 montres restantes</span>
        <span class="live-ticker-item"><span class="t-emoji">🚚</span> Expédition en 24h</span>
        <span class="live-ticker-item"><span class="t-emoji">🎁</span> Livraison gratuite</span>
        <span class="live-ticker-item"><span class="t-emoji">↩️</span> Retour gratuit 60 jours</span>
